          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ようこそ！"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "MeowPassword makes passwords that are strong, easy to read aloud, and — with MeowGram — hideable inside cat photos.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "MeowPassword erstellt Passwörter, die stark und leicht vorzulesen sind – und sich mit MeowGram in Katzenfotos verstecken lassen."
          }
        },
        "en-GB": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "MeowPassword makes passwords that are strong, easy to read aloud, and — with MeowGram — hideable inside cat photos."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "MeowPassword crée des mots de passe robustes et faciles à lire à voix haute — et, avec MeowGram, dissimulables dans des photos de chats."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "MeowPasswordは、強くて声に出して読みやすいパスワードを作ります。MeowGramを使えば猫の写真の中に隠すこともできます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Conjures five strong passwords and crowns the highest-scoring winner. Tap the clipboard to copy it.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Zaubert fünf starke Passwörter und kürt den Sieger mit der höchsten Punktzahl. Tippe auf die Zwischenablage, um es zu kopieren."
          }
        },
        "en-GB": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Conjures five strong passwords and crowns the highest-scoring winner. Tap the clipboard to copy it."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Crée cinq mots de passe robustes et couronne le gagnant au meilleur score. Touchez le presse-papiers pour le copier."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "強いパスワードを5つ生み出し、最高スコアの勝者を選びます。クリップボードをタップしてコピーしましょう。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Opens the cat-mail studio — hide a secret message inside an ordinary-looking cat picture, or decode one you were sent.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Öffnet das Katzenpost-Studio – verstecke eine geheime Nachricht in einem gewöhnlich aussehenden Katzenbild oder dekodiere eine erhaltene."
          }
        },
        "en-GB": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Opens the cat-mail studio — hide a secret message inside an ordinary-looking cat picture, or decode one you were sent."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ouvre le studio de chat-courrier — cachez un message secret dans une photo de chat d'apparence ordinaire, ou décodez-en un que l'on vous a envoyé."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "猫メールスタジオを開きます。ふつうに見える猫の写真に秘密のメッセージを隠したり、届いたものをデコードしたりできます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Paste any password to score its strength from 0 to 10, with a verdict.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Füge ein beliebiges Passwort ein, um seine Stärke von 0 bis 10 mit einem Urteil zu bewerten."
          }
        },
        "en-GB": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Paste any password to score its strength from 0 to 10, with a verdict."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Collez n'importe quel mot de passe pour noter sa force de 0 à 10, avec un verdict."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "好きなパスワードを貼り付けると、強さを0〜10で採点し、評価を返します。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Dial in how many numbers and symbols to mix in, and the maximum length.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Stelle ein, wie viele Zahlen und Symbole eingemischt werden und wie lang das Passwort maximal ist."
          }
        },
        "en-GB": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Dial in how many numbers and symbols to mix in, and the maximum length."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Réglez le nombre de chiffres et de symboles à mélanger, ainsi que la longueur maximale."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "混ぜる数字と記号の数、そして最大の長さを調整できます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "MeowGram hides a secret message inside an ordinary-looking cat photo. Here's how to send one.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "MeowGram versteckt eine geheime Nachricht in einem gewöhnlich aussehenden Katzenfoto. So verschickst du eines."
          }
        },
        "en-GB": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "MeowGram hides a secret message inside an ordinary-looking cat photo. Here's how to send one."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "MeowGram cache un message secret dans une photo de chat d'apparence ordinaire. Voici comment en envoyer un."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "MeowGramは、ふつうに見える猫の写真の中に秘密のメッセージを隠します。送り方はこちら。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "COMPOSE hides a message; DECODE reveals one you were sent. Tap to switch anytime.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ERSTELLEN versteckt eine Nachricht; DEKODIEREN zeigt eine erhaltene. Tippe zum Wechseln jederzeit."
          }
        },
        "en-GB": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "COMPOSE hides a message; DECODE reveals one you were sent. Tap to switch anytime."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "COMPOSER cache un message ; DÉCODER révèle celui qu'on vous a envoyé. Touchez pour basculer à tout moment."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "「作成」はメッセージを隠し、「デコード」は届いたものを表示します。いつでもタップで切り替えられます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Type the message you want to smuggle. The counter shows how much still fits.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tippe die Nachricht ein, die du schmuggeln willst. Der Zähler zeigt, wie viel noch passt."
          }
        },
        "en-GB": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Type the message you want to smuggle. The counter shows how much still fits."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Saisissez le message à faire passer. Le compteur indique ce qui tient encore."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "こっそり送りたいメッセージを入力してください。カウンターに残りの容量が表示されます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Optionally lock it. GENERATE mints a cat-name key that's easy to read aloud to your recipient.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Optional sperren. ERZEUGEN erstellt einen Katzennamen-Schlüssel, der sich leicht vorlesen lässt."
          }
        },
        "en-GB": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Optionally lock it. GENERATE mints a cat-name key that's easy to read aloud to your recipient."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Verrouillez-le si vous voulez. GÉNÉRER crée une clé en noms de chats, facile à lire à voix haute au destinataire."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "任意でロックできます。「生成」は、相手に読み上げやすい猫の名前のキーを作ります。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Choose the cat that carries your message — swipe sideways to browse all 100.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Wähle die Katze, die deine Nachricht trägt – wische zur Seite, um alle 100 zu durchstöbern."
          }
        },
        "en-GB": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Choose the cat that carries your message — swipe sideways to browse all 100."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Choisissez le chat qui porte votre message — balayez sur le côté pour parcourir les 100."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "メッセージを運ぶ猫を選んでください。横にスワイプすると100匹すべてを見られます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Writes the hidden message into the cat, then SHARE or SAVE the innocent-looking photo.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Schreibt die versteckte Nachricht in die Katze, dann TEILEN oder SPEICHERN des harmlos wirkenden Fotos."
          }
        },
        "en-GB": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Writes the hidden message into the cat, then SHARE or SAVE the innocent-looking photo."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Inscrit le message caché dans le chat, puis PARTAGER ou ENREGISTRER la photo d'apparence innocente."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "隠しメッセージを猫に書き込み、なにげない写真を「シェア」または「保存」します。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Got a cat photo from someone? Reveal the message hidden inside it.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ein Katzenfoto von jemandem bekommen? Enthülle die darin versteckte Nachricht."
