            "state": "translated",
            "value": "貼り付けるものがありません — まずMeowGram画像をコピーしてください。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Hiss! A kitten could paw this one open! Try a meowpass-generated password instead!": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Fauch! Das knackt schon ein Kätzchen mit einer Pfote! Nimm lieber ein von meowpass erzeugtes Passwort!"
          }
        },
        "en-GB": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Hiss! A kitten could paw this one open! Try a meowpass-generated password instead!"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Fff ! Un chaton ouvrirait ça d'un coup de patte ! Prenez plutôt un mot de passe généré par meowpass !"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "シャー！こんなの子猫でも前足でパッと開けちゃう！meowpassで作ったパスワードを使ってね！"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Meow... this string is a bit too easy for a clever cat to guess.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Miau… diese Zeichenkette ist für eine schlaue Katze etwas zu leicht zu erraten."
          }
        },
        "en-GB": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Meow... this string is a bit too easy for a clever cat to guess."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Miaou… cette chaîne est un peu trop facile à deviner pour un chat malin."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ニャー…この文字列は賢い猫にはちょっと簡単に当てられちゃう。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Not bad, hooman! This string has decent whisker-resistance.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Nicht schlecht, Mensch! Diese Zeichenkette hat ordentlichen Schnurrhaar-Widerstand."
          }
        },
        "en-GB": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Not bad, hooman! This string has decent whisker-resistance."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Pas mal, humain ! Cette chaîne a une résistance de moustaches correcte."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "なかなかやるね、人間！この文字列はまずまずのヒゲ耐性があるよ。"
          }
